Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.67,0:00:34.88,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,one two three.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:39.18,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,undead tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.22,0:00:41.68,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,what truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.93,0:00:45.64,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,I’ll come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:56.61,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,I see that bright light.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.57,0:01:02.95,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,this is all I have
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.66,0:01:05.41,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,what did you say？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.62,0:01:07.50,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.12,0:01:12.09,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,why do you say？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:17.59,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,刃を砥ぐ、微睡む
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.59,0:01:20.80,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,survive of vision
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.80,0:01:24.43,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,詩と快楽は未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.68,0:01:26.56,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,I got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.56,0:01:28.64,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,I was lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.85,0:01:32.52,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,survive of vision
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.52,0:01:35.69,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,final white heaven
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.90,0:01:39.36,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,さあ奪い合うよ傷を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.74,0:01:41.24,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,I don’t know why.
